Studies show that competition improves your performance. So why aren't you studying for coding interviews this way?

This app lets you LeetCode competitively against your friends. (Any number of friends!)

Compete against friends, race to finish, and review each-others code to learn the best ways to attack those difficult coding problems.

Can you beat your friends?
